      "content": "i get that, but \"resilience\" just feels like a way to sugarcoat the inevitable. it feels so selfish to just keep going and consuming when i know the math doesn't add up. like, how can anyone justify living a whole life knowing it's all just leading to a massive collapse? it feels more logical to just... not be a part of it.",
